comment: Gortat (WAS) and Zeller (CHA) engage briefly with one another during rebounding.
Dudley (WAS) sets the screen on Walker (CHA) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Williams (CHA) makes incidental contact with Wall (WAS) that does not affect his RSBQ.
Zeller (CHA) legally contests Gortat's (WAS) shot attempt, making incidental "high-five" contact after the release.
Batum (CHA) commits a take foul on Temple (WAS).
After communicating with the Replay Center, the officials determined that the foul by Batum (CHA) did not meet the criteria for a clear path foul.
Sessions (WAS) maintains a legal guarding position on Lin's (CHA) drive.
Wall (WAS) makes contact with Zeller's (CHA) arm that affects his shot attempt.
Walker (CHA) and Dudley (WAS) briefly engage and separate away from the ball.
LHH shows Walker (CHA) gathers the ball on his right foot and is then permitted two steps. He comes down on his left foot and then right foot, and then takes the shot.
Batum (CHA) makes incidental contact with Sessions as he jumps to deflect the pass.
Williams (CHA) sets the screen on Temple (WAS) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Walker (CHA) dislodges Dudley (WAS) from behind and affects his ability to secure the loose ball.
Oubre Jr. (WAS) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Williams' (CHA) driving shot attempt.
Lin (CHA) commits a take foul on Wall (WAS).
Wall (WAS) makes contact with the ball before it has reached its apex and is still on its upward flight toward the basket.
